videos.description: Jake Browning finds Quinten Pounds for a 40-yard catch to put the Huskies at Oregon State's 24 yard line.
videos.headline: Washington gets into Oregon State territory with big play

videos.description: Jake Browning's 11-yard touchdown run gives the Washington a 7-0 lead over Oregon State.
videos.headline: Jake Browning gets the Huskies on the board with TD run

videos.description: Jake Browning connects with Dante Pettis for a five-yard touchdown pass to give the Huskies a two-touchdown lead over the Beavers.
videos.headline: Pettis out-leaps defender for TD grab

videos.description: Greg Gaines recovers the fumble after Burr-Kirven forces the ball loose.
videos.headline: Washington forces first Oregon State turnover

videos.description: David Morris picks off Jake Browning and returns it for six yards to his own 30-yard line.
videos.headline: Jake Browning's pass is intercepted by Oregon State

videos.description: Myles Gaskin escapes tackles for a 32-yard touchdown run to put the Huskies up 28-0.
videos.headline: Gaskin breaks tackles for TD run

videos.description: Jake Browning throws a 15-yard touchdown pass to Dante Pettis to increase Washington's lead to 35.
videos.headline: Jake Browning connects with Pettis for a third time for a TD

videos.description: Sean McGrew finds a hole for a four-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Huskies find the end zone again with rushing TD

videos.description: Jake Browning throws for 293 yards and accounts for four total scores as No. 6 Washington routs Oregon State 42-7.
videos.headline: Washington crushes Oregon State
